  <div class="be-section">── PROS & CONS (2-MARK ANSWERS) ─────────────────────────</div>
  <div class="be-row"><span class="be-key">Benefit ✅</span><span class="be-val">Shorter, cleaner code for naturally recursive problems</span></div>
  <div class="be-row"><span class="be-key">Drawback ❌</span><span class="be-val">Uses more memory — each call creates a new stack frame</span></div>
